The palm-fringed Ashtamudi Lake is perhaps your best real-time reference to the image that the land of Kerala conjures up in your mind. A stay at the Raviz Ashtamudi enjoying the traditional architecture, the cuisine, the Ayurvedic rejuvenation & the houseboat cruise is what you need to touch the soul of God’s Own Country.
